Sum of Even Numbers till N
Send Feedback
Given a number N, print sum of all even numbers from 1 to N.
Input Format :
Integer N
Output Format :
Required Sum 
Sample Input 1 :
 6
Sample Output 1 :
12
-----------------------------------------------------
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main(){
    int n,sum=0;
    cin>>n;
    int number=0;
    while(number<=n){
        sum=sum+number;
		number=number+2;
    }
    cout<<sum;
}
---------------------------------------------
